WEBVTT

00:00:59.360 --> 00:01:03.696
e ji m mkpịsịaka hichapụ otjize n'ihu isi m
m wee sekpuru ala

00:01:03.720 --> 00:01:05.576
wee metụ mkpịsị aka n'aja,

00:01:05.600 --> 00:01:08.056
na-agbari
ụrọ na-esi isi ọma n'ime ya.

00:01:08.080 --> 00:01:09.960
M wee jiri nwayọ kwuo "Daalụ,"

00:01:11.040 --> 00:01:14.016
Ọ bụ ije kilomita
n'ogologo ụzọ ọzara gbara ọchịchịrị.

00:01:14.040 --> 00:01:16.800
Ụgbọ nje m ka na arụ ọrụ 
Aga m eru ebe ahụ n'oge

00:01:18.080 --> 00:01:20.816
A kwụụrụ m ọto,
kwụsịnata, wee mechie anya m.

00:01:20.840 --> 00:01:24.736
Ugbua, ibu ndụ m niile
na arụgide m n'ubu.

00:01:24.760 --> 00:01:27.976
Nke a bụ izizi
m na emere onwe m isiike

00:01:28.000 --> 00:01:29.576
na ndụ m niile.


00:01:29.600 --> 00:01:33.020
Ana m ahapụ n'etiti abalị,
ma ha amaghịị.